data.description: REDUCED!  "AS IS".   FIRST HOME OR DOWNSIZING OR RENTAL PROPERTY.  ADORABLE masonry BUNGALOW with BIG TICKET ITEMS ALREADY DONE!  Main roof Dec 2021.  Family room and garage roofs 2014. CENTRAL HEAT & AIR with NEW DUCT WORK May 2016, WINDOWS 2009, WATER HEATER April 2023. 6 panel doors. Kitchen & bath plumbing updated July 2023.  TERRAZZO in main living area and family room, under carpet.   Install heat/air in FLORIDA ROOM adds an additional 150 sq ft for instant equity.  Plus another 269 sq ft of COVERED PORCH off family room to cool off in back.  PERFECT SETTING extending your living and entertainment space for friends & family. Large STORAGE ROOM off covered porch. FENCED YARD.   NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE (zone X)- non evacuation zone.  LARGE main bedroom.  Situated close to downtown St Pete, 275 to Tampa and Sarasota, Restaurants, Shopping, Gyms, Hospitals and more.  Beautiful beaches are a short drive away.  ENDLESS POSSIBILITIES to make this adorable  conveniently located bungalow your home.  PAVERS in driveway.  Parking and entrance to attached one car garage is off alley.  Washer/dryer hook ups in garage. For an AFFORDABLE PRICE POINT in a very pricey market you can enjoy a great neighborhood &  all that St Pete has to offer.  Convert garage.  So many possibilities with solid masonry property with big ticket items already to go. See realtor remarks.
